cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to predict lead close rates. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to gather data from social media and search engines, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The use of deep learning models and boosting performance of lead scoring models suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves predictive modeling, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy concerns in lead generation, which could make it relevant to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
